name: MedicalTest
description: Tests for the Medical provider in the BaseFaker class, focusing on various medical-related data generation.

test_cases.name: testDiagnosisCodeUS
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of diagnosis codes for the US locale, ensuring they match the expected ICD-10-CM format.

test_cases.name: testDiagnosisCodeAU
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of diagnosis codes for the Australian locale, ensuring they match the expected ICD-10-AM format.

test_cases.name: testDiagnosisCodeNotAustraliaNorUS
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of diagnosis codes for locales other than Australia and the US, ensuring they match the expected ICD-10 format.

test_cases.name: testProcedureCodes
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of procedure codes, ensuring they match the expected ICD-10-PCS format.
